    "This can be done by a single expert or a (mostly small) team of experts.",
    "This approach requires limited resources.",
    "An important benefit is, in contrast to relying on what is available in existing literature, the level of detail in the DCT specifications can be as extensive as needed.",
    "This enables a detailed specification of the direct link between the construct definitions and instructions on how to use them in research (which is often lacking in existing literature).",
    "Given that this approach relies on a limited number of experts, this might result in a narrow view on the psychological construct of interest."
